## Orders [/order]

### Create new order [POST]
+ Request
   + Headers 
  
            Authorization: KEY your_api_key
   + Body

            {
                "customer": "Jan Kowalski",
                "comment": "4p. sala raum D",
                "vendorId": 1,
                "products": [
                    {
                        "productId": 1,
                        "amount": 1
                    },
                    {
                        "productId": 2,
                        "amount": 1
                    }
                ]
            }
   
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "orderId": 123
        }
        
        
